tab-title: DJ Club @ OSU - Schedule an Event
title: Schedule an Event
description:
Ready to take your event to the next level? In addition to being a teaching group, DJ Club is comprised of some of the most talented DJs at Ohio State. You've heard our DJs at Midway, Ethyl, Dahlia, Big Bar, Breakaway Music Festival, and opening for national touring artists.

We pride ourselves on being different than any other local DJ company, and our superior skill puts us in a category separate from the rest of the Columbus-Area DJs. Book us for your next event and see for yourself.
